{
  "text": "We found that intra-rater agreement for the indexes considered was excellent, despite a time interval of 5 months between the two evaluations. Inter-rater agreement ranged between substantial and excellent, despite only providing a brief explanatory session to the resident before rating. These results are in agreement with the data on reliability on semi-quantitative measure of MC recently published by Wang et al. [CITATION_1] .",
